NOISE STABILITY: ARROW'S THEOREM QUANTIFIED
======================================================================
  Classical Arrow: no non-dictatorial social welfare function satisfies IIA
  Quantitative Arrow (Kalai): low-influence SCFs are noise-unstable
  Our result: H has UNIFORM low influence => maximally noise-STABLE
  This means: H-optimal tournaments are the MOST stable rankings

